b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":1870,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Gala Dragalia Is Now Live!","message":"<div>Gala Dragalia went live at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1609135200\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>What are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe initial appearance rate for 5\\u2605 adventurers and dragons is boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5\\u2605 summon or 5\\u2605 featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Newly added featured dragon:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Gala Reborn Zephyr (wind)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Gala Dragalia appearance rates:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 total: 6.00%<\/div><div>5\\u2605 featured total: 0.80% (Dragons: 0.80%)<\/div><div>5\\u2605 standard total: 5.20% (Adventurers: 3.00%, Dragons: 2.20%)<\/div><div>4\\u2605 standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%, Dragons: 7.45%)<\/div><div>3\\u2605 standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1609135200\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1609394399\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Get a closer look at the newly added featured dragon below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Featured dragon:<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/60e5be4356d184ba3de6142f06fa5054.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>369<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>126<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>1,295<\/span>\\n                <\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Dragon Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>Through the belief of the people of the plains,<br>Zephyr has been reborn. Freed from the noxious<br>miasma eating away at his body, his prudence is<br>now tempered with an unwavering will and an<br>open mind.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/930e79020344385658dbc5220432cb572.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Howling Fury<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDeals wind damage to the target and nearby<br>enemies. If the user is targeting an enemy<br>and not using a skill when their remaining<br>shapeshift time runs out, this skill will be used<br>automatically, regardless of whether or not<br>the skill gauge is filled.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t<\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span><span>(Wind) Strength +70%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind: <br>increases strength by 70%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/65863989132db80658f5d919573c14e92.png\\"><\/span><span>(Wind) Wrath of the Plains II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind:<br>adds 30% to the modifier applied to damage<br>against water-attuned enemies for 45 seconds<br>every time the dragon gauge fills by 10%.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>this ability will not activate again for 5 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe stats shown here represent the dragon at maximum level, maximum bond, and fully unbound. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Note: For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1609135200,"prev_article_id":"1865","next_article_id":"1873","image_path":"","update_time":1608617518}}}'